title: Ukraine 2014: Odessa May 2 rescue service 101 phone recording
description:
Phone recording from rescue service 101 on May 2 2014.

Multiple people are calling to tell about fire on Kulikovo Pole square and asking for fire service to come.

At first operator replies that the fire is only on tents on the open area and that there is no danger.

Later people start telling that fire has moved to the House of Trade Unions, operator tells that she already knows everything and that she has sent a fire-car, but makes no action.

People start telling that there are people inside burning building and asking for firemen and police to come, operator replies that they know, makes no action
